      },
      {
        "q": "Which equation represents $y$ is inversely proportional to the square of $x$?",
        "q_zh": "下列哪个方程表示 $y$ 与 $x$ 的平方成反比？",
        "o": [
          "y = kx^2",
          "y = k / x",
