  {
    "id": "kp-2.7-01",
    "section": "2.7",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Solving Quadratic Equations by Factorising",
    "title_zh": "用因式分解法解二次方程",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "A **quadratic equation** is an equation of the form $ax^2 + bx + c = 0$. \n\nTo solve by factorising:\n1. Ensure the equation equals **zero**.\n2. Factorise the quadratic expression into two brackets.\n3. Set each bracket to zero (Null Factor Law) and solve for $x$.\n\nA quadratic equation usually has **two solutions**.",
      "zh": "**二次方程**是形式为 $ax^2 + bx + c = 0$ 的方程。\n\n用因式分解法求解：\n1. 确保方程等号一侧为**零**。\n2. 将二次代数式分解为两个括号相乘。\n3. 令每个括号分别为零（零乘积性质）并解出 $x$。\n\n二次方程通常有**两个解**。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-solve-quad-fact",
        "label": "Solve quadratic by factorising",
        "label_zh": "用因式分解法解二次方程",
        "description": "Factorise and solve equations of the form $x^2 + bx + c = 0$.",
        "description_zh": "分解并求解 $x^2 + bx + c = 0$ 形式的方程。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-solve-quad-fact",
        "question": "Solve $x^2 - 5x + 6 = 0$.",
        "question_zh": "解方程 $x^2 - 5x + 6 = 0$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Factorise the expression. We need numbers that multiply to $+6$ and add to $-5$. These are $-2$ and $-3$.\n$(x - 2)(x - 3) = 0$\n\n**Step 2:** Set each factor to zero.\n$x - 2 = 0 \\Rightarrow x = 2$\n$x - 3 = 0 \\Rightarrow x = 3$\n\n**Answer:** $x = 2, x = 3$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 因式分解。我们需要积为 $+6$ 且和为 $-5$ 的两个数。这两个数是 $-2$ 和 $-3$。\n$(x - 2)(x - 3) = 0$\n\n**步骤2：** 令每个因式为零。\n$x - 2 = 0 \\Rightarrow x = 2$\n$x - 3 = 0 \\Rightarrow x = 3$\n\n**答案：** $x = 2, x = 3$",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1F/Jan/2021"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-solve-quad-fact",
        "question": "Solve $x^2 + 4x = 21$.",
        "question_zh": "解方程 $x^2 + 4x = 21$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Rearrange to equal zero.\n$x^2 + 4x - 21 = 0$\n\n**Step 2:** Factorise. Multipliers of $-21$ that add to $+4$ are $+7$ and $-3$.\n$(x + 7)(x - 3) = 0$\n\n**Step 3:** Solve.\n$x = -7$ or $x = 3$\n\n**Answer:** $x = -7, x = 3$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 移项使等式右侧为零。\n$x^2 + 4x - 21 = 0$\n\n**步骤2：** 因式分解。$-21$ 的因数中和为 $+4$ 的是 $+7$ 和 $-3$。\n$(x + 7)(x - 3) = 0$\n\n**步骤3：** 求解。\n$x = -7$ 或 $x = 3$\n\n**答案：** $x = -7, x = 3$",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/2H/June/2017"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "Solve $x^2 - 9 = 0$.",
