  {
    "id": "kp-2.8-01",
    "section": "2.8",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Linear Inequalities",
    "title_zh": "一次不等式",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "An **inequality** shows that one expression is greater than or less than another using symbols: $>$ (greater than), $<$ (less than), $\\ge$ (greater than or equal to), and $\\le$ (less than or equal to).\n\nSolve them just like equations, but **IMPORTANT**: If you multiply or divide both sides by a **negative number**, you must **flip the inequality sign**.\n\nSolutions can be represented on a **number line**: an open circle $\\circ$ for $>$ or $<$, and a solid circle $\\bullet$ for $\\ge$ or $\\le$.",
      "zh": "**不等式**使用符号表示一个表达式大于或小于另一个表达式：$>$（大于）、$<$（小于）、$\\ge$（大于或等于）和 $\\le$（小于或等于）。\n\n求解方法与方程类似，但**重要提示**：如果两边同时乘以或除以一个**负数**，必须**反转不等号的方向**。\n\n解集可以用**数轴**表示：空心圆圈 $\\circ$ 表示 $>$ 或 $<$，实心圆点 $\\bullet$ 表示 $\\ge$ 或 $\\le$。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-solve-inequality",
        "label": "Solve and represent inequalities",
        "label_zh": "求解并表示不等式",
        "description": "Solve linear inequalities and list integer solutions or show on a number line.",
        "description_zh": "解一次不等式，列出整数解或在数轴上表示。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-solve-inequality",
        "question": "Solve $5x - 7 < 3x + 9$.",
        "question_zh": "解不等式 $5x - 7 < 3x + 9$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Subtract $3x$ from both sides.\n$2x - 7 < 9$\n\n**Step 2:** Add 7 to both sides.\n$2x < 16$\n\n**Step 3:** Divide by 2.\n$x < 8$\n\n**Answer:** $x < 8$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 两边同时减去 $3x$。\n$2x - 7 < 9$\n\n**步骤2：** 两边同时加上 7。\n$2x < 16$\n\n**步骤3：** 两边同时除以 2。\n$x < 8$\n\n**答案：** $x < 8$",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/2F/Jan/2021"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-solve-inequality",
        "question": "Solve the inequality $10 - 2x \\le 4$.",
        "question_zh": "解不等式 $10 - 2x \\le 4$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Subtract 10 from both sides.\n$-2x \\le -6$\n\n**Step 2:** Divide by $-2$ and **flip the sign**.\n$x \\ge \\frac{-6}{-2}$\n$x \\ge 3$\n\n**Answer:** $x \\ge 3$",
